{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"8":"The Chapters Regarding Zakat"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1833,"arabicnumber":1833,"text":"২/১৮৩৩। জাবির ইবনু ‘আবদুল্লাহ্ (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। তিনি বলেন, রসূলুল্লাহ সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম বলেছেনঃ ষাট সা-এ এক ওয়াসক।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Very Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":8,"hadith":51}}]}